      <ID>4</ID>
      <DefaultText>Introdução educada.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>5</ID>
      <DefaultText>[Player Name],

Do you remember your training under [url=glossary:bleden mark]Bleden Mark[/url]? I remember mine - funny to think that you and I are about a century apart, but to [url=glossary:bleden mark]Bleden Mark[/url], we are all children.

I'm now the oldest of the Court's 'children' and I've seen much in my time. It's probably for the best everyone assumes I'm old, harmless, and worth shuffling away in the archives... if I were scrutinized too closely, I'm sure [url=glossary:tunon]Tunon[/url] would find I've grown lax in my spoiled old age...

Part of why I am where I am is that I've kept my head down - you appear to be doing the opposite. In some regards, this is beyond your control - you were chosen for the honor of proclaiming [url=glossary:kyros]Kyros[/url]' Edicts - twice! To decline would have meant death, but to accept means to be placed on the stage for all to see.

[url=glossary:kyros]Kyros[/url]' most powerful weapon is not the [url=glossary:edict]Edict[/url], it's her ability to hand us rope that we willingly use to hang ourselves - never forget this.

There are numerous questions nestled in your request - what is it you wish to know most? Focus your inquiry and I will answer as best I can.

-Fatebinder Myothis</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>6</ID>
      <DefaultText>Caro Fatebinder Myothis,

Eu escrevo para você a pedido do meu colega e professor, Fatebinder Rhogalus. Ele encontrou-se desprovido de respostas (uma condição rara para ele) e sugeriu que você pode ser a única fonte das respostas que procuro.

Se você perdoar a imposição, isso significaria muito para aprender o que você sabe sobre os Editos e a magia das Torres. A Montanha Pináculo das Camadas despertou para a minha presença - um evento que ocorreu momentos depois de eu ter resolvido um [url=glossary:edict]Edict[/url] de [url=glossary:kyros]Kyros[/url] - então é fundamental que eu aprenda o que aconteceu comigo, e o que tudo isso significa.

Agradeço antecipadamente por sua consideração e sabedoria.

-Fatebinder [nome do jogador]</DefaultText>
